reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Look no further! This is the one!!
reviews.reviewText: I don’t like to review products, I tend to read the reviews and make a decision based on what people have to say and pictures they post. This is the first time I felt I should be one of those people! This organizer is easy to put together, similar to a jigsaw puzzle, just slide it in and your done, if you want to sturdy, you can use double stick tape or a little e600 and the puzzle piece will stay put. I don’t know if the design was updated, but I did not have an issue with the Apple Watch charger fitting into its slot, it actually fit in like a glove. The back has plenty of room for my MacBook or iPad, the drawer is a decent size, fits all of my night time lotions and potions. The slot for the phone and shelf does come out of its slot easily, but e600 glue worked like a charm. The organizer has a high end look and feel. It is not flimsy or lightweight. I highly recommend this product!!

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Looks good, but Apple Watch charger doesn’t fit
reviews.reviewText: This organizer looks good and goes with our decor. It was easy to put together and has lots of storage as was needed. I just received it so we’ll see about it’s longevity. The biggest issue is that the cut out for the apple watch charger doesn’t fit an Apple Watch charger. I’ll need to make it bigger. I should have noticed by the pictures that there is no cable management to speak of, so I’ll need to remedy that also.
